description: This file defines the LibraryEntry data class and the LibraryService class which interacts with an API client to fetch paginated library data.

classes.name: LibraryEntry
classes.description: Represents an entry in the user's library, containing book details and identifiers.

classes.name: LibraryService
classes.description: Provides methods to access library data from an API endpoint, including listing entries with pagination.

methods.name: LibraryEntry.fromJson
methods.description: Factory constructor to create a LibraryEntry instance from a JSON map.

methods.name: LibraryService.list
methods.description: Fetches a paginated list of LibraryEntry objects from the API, with optional query filtering.
